Package: basen
Type: Package
Title: Basen: Base-level abundance estimation with species-assigned evidence using nanopore
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Heewon", "Seo", , "Heewon.Seo@ucalgary.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Calculates genome-size-normalized species-level relative abundance
    from Kraken2 classification outputs. The package explicitly accounts
    for variable read lengths by extracting species-specific k-mer
    assignments and normalizing this evidence by reference genome sizes.
    It also includes read-level k-mer compositional filtering to identify
    and exclude ambiguous classifications prior to quantification, and
    provides utilities for cross-sample aggregation and median-ratio size
    factor calculation.
